{"tid":1519570,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"我之前是在香港鳩嗚的，而我去鳩嗚的原則是","createTime":"2019-08-30T15:12:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T15:48:08.000Z","uid":34489,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"07317523964fdbcf5cb3e5dba65442c5c84cc51b","tid":1519570,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:12:40.000Z","msg":"「幹你娘塞爆」<br />\n沒錯，就是幹你娘塞爆，老子才不管甚麼香港九龍新界的，每次去的鳩嗚就是姬芭一大塞。通知親戚朋友，行人路塞到馬路，馬路塞到地鐵站，塞了一個站再塞另一個，跟把整個香港的路跟遊行沒兩樣。<br />\n<br />\n我還記得，我那年鳩嗚80天，經理跑來跟我說，這兩個月遊行人數一千萬，你有頭緒嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我他媽的怎麼會知道。"},{"pid":"29acc164474f5be4ee3c895cee334cf95276ea41","tid":1519570,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:14:51.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0s2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=8025b394\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 公海</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0s2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=e925e638\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 宣傳</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"h